ℹ️🔤imprt_npy_tmsh_prm↩️hd=Sphr(0.5,2)↩️bd=Cyl(0.25,2)↩️la=Cyl(0.125,1.5)↩️ra=Cyl(0.125,1.5)↩️ll=Cyl(0.125,2)↩️rl=Cyl(0.125,2)↩️xfrm=trimesh.transformations.rotation_matrix↩️π=np.pi↩️🔁[hd^0,0,3.5,bd^0,0,1.5,la^(-.75,0,2.5),ra^(.75,0,2.5),ll^(-.25,0,.5),rl^(.25,0,.5)]↩️🔄[-π/6,(0,1,0),la,ra,π/6,ll,rl]↩️🎨=human_form=trimesh.util.concat([hd,bd,la,ra,ll,rl])↩️📏=scale=0.1/human_form.bounds[:,2].ptp()↩️human_form.apply_scale(scale)↩️💾=human_form.export('human_form.stl')
